  "title": "AB03 -Production Baker – Bakery Services (Junior)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Junior Baker</strong><br />Gross Salary: $2000 - $2200<br />Working Days & Hours: 6 Days | 9hrs/day<br />Working Location: Tai Seng</p><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare, mix, and bake doughs, pastries, bread, cakes, and other baked items according to standard recipes.</li><li>Measure and weigh ingredients accurately.</li><li>Operate baking equipment such as mixers, ovens, sheeters, proofers, and portioning tools.</li><li>Ensure consistent product quality, taste, and appearance.</li><li>Assist in R&D for new recipes or seasonal items (if required).</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>With relevant education or at least 1 year of working experience in bakery</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
